RawLine: ITEM_700056_Tip,將令牌給守衛看，可前往第二域。令牌正面有白虎紋樣，並附有『木櫃金鎖，平衡之謎，兩端皆虎，即達平衡。』這段文字。,将令牌给守卫看，可前往第二域。令牌正面有白虎纹样，并附有『木柜金锁，平衡之谜，两端皆虎，即达平衡。』这段文字。

Items.mt: Show the token to the guard and you can go to the second domain. The token has a white tiger pattern on the front, and is accompanied by the words, "Wooden cabinet and golden lock, the mystery of balance, both ends of the tiger, that is, balance. This text.
